1K urethane base coat paint. Easy to spray, backed by Spectral Paints' color match guarantee. Must test color match before painting.

Finishing with clear coat is required. We recommend our 2K 4:1 Clear Coat Kit. Our 1K spray can clear coat makes your job even easier!

Surface must be primed or must be previously painted and sufficiently prepped before applying Spectral Paints 1K Urethane Basecoat.

On raw plastic, use our Adhesion Promoter or our Adhesion Promoter Spray.

Product comes UNREDUCED. Must reduce using Urethane Reducer. After reducing, customers will have 2 pints (1 quart) of sprayable product, approximately 75-100sqft of coverage depending on color.

All products are final sale. Please check your color before starting your job. Color doesn't match? Reach out to us!
